{"tid":1338851,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"咪撚再擺散紙呀！買多幾張車飛呀！","createTime":"2019-07-21T14:44:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T15:21:56.000Z","uid":39205,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f8cee65fb1a0ef5ec33ada1790a548047fddb9fd","tid":1338851,"uid":39205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T14:44:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有閒錢嘅直接買多幾張飛啦！<br />\n買完攝係個screen個到等人攞啦，再唔係唔趕嘅留低派比人都得！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n買張飛去隔離一個站$5蚊架咋！拎廿蚊紙可以買四張架啦！<br />\n拎左張飛入左閘搭到去邊都得架，搭搭下車跌左張飛唔犯法架，行去票務站講返係邊到上車比返錢就得架啦！<br />\n舉個例子你係北角上車寶琳落車你比返個程車錢得架啦！<br />\n<br />\n見到好多人都好似唔敢拎上面啲錢咁，啲錢啲車飛我地放得低預左比人拎架啦，比自己人拎好過留比地鐵呀，唔好怕羞啦分秒必爭呀！"},{"pid":"4bcd9236f812c7dc7298644ca3475e4b5cc3b17e","tid":1338851,"uid":267311,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T14:46:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d9fbe85d4b685047572853f87b1a11425a33e5b","tid":1338851,"uid":102185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T14:47:29.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8ceaa457729f26ffb050d4827fa950cc4941b401","tid":1338851,"uid":272587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T14:47:37.000Z","msg":"求下大家拎 前線可能唔得閒睇所以如果仲係個度既提下佢地拎呀！咪撚益港鐵"},{"pid":"4f069f037ced4a7d7a02807ee30e8917c258e170","tid":1338851,"uid":39205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T14:47:51.000Z","msg":"推呀！你搵散紙買飛不如直接拎張飛入左閘先啦！"},{"pid":"a7ad7fedbb4cd971519c3eebaed1b88f0cafece9","tid":1338851,"uid":168703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T14:51:27.000Z","msg":"推呀！比仲係現場嘅人知道呀！"},{"pid":"2f9d5d296438d39762674527d66c067b6da83735","tid":1338851,"uid":168703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T14:58:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a92324ace7257fb9ef4c02c77bdcc0a7cb7e3ea0","tid":1338851,"uid":275475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T15:05:43.000Z","msg":"為節省時間<br />\n直接入閘！！！<br />\n如果見唔到飛 趕不及買<br />\n<br />\n直接衝入閘門啦<br />\n聽講好多人不見銀包<br />\n趕住回家煲湯"},{"pid":"8d2bae9619b88b173f82f0762127b4b2339c21d4","tid":1338851,"uid":282902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T15:07:08.000Z","msg":"買票機頂上有飛"},{"pid":"c88840a9fc5362d43d556864fc10cb05802bf780","tid":1338851,"uid":39205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T15:21:56.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母元朗啲黑社會係咪痴撚左線"}]}